snippet.textDisplay:
Hi, trying my best to translate !

O beloved,I will flow the river Jaji (River's name) with my heart's blood,
And turn it into a River of Blood, my Love.

My Love when you get married, you will bathe in "haldi-uptan"
Your entire body will be besmeared in haldi-uptan.

Dont say I'll marry you just by my Tip-Top Look! For, dear, mine is a rain-dripping hut. You'll catch cold-fever by soaking water.
O dear, My heart will be broken seeing you go away.

Sorry for the so unpoetic translation !
snippet.textOriginal:
Hi, trying my best to translate !

O beloved,I will flow the river Jaji (River's name) with my heart's blood,
